      <div class="tier-row">
        <span class="tier-badge reality">Reality</span>
        <div class="tier-content">
          <strong>0.3–0.4g per pound — where most men actually are</strong>
          <span>The typical intake. Looks fine until you do the math.</span>
        </div>
